{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}eighteen New Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. They come from Stepney. My wife's mother lived at Stepney before she moved in to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Canning{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Town{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. See? And - they had no father, her father died - oh, quite a - many years before - her mother come to 
