t up - up a lot of other books for to be bound. Bring 'em back to the shop. Well, I used to get - six shillings a week. Penny if I was a good boy. And - tips I used to have give me - and - I - I - I used to have enough to take the missus out to the pictur
es - weekend, yes. So we used to go up the threepenny rush. They called it the threepenny rush in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Canning{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Town{\*\xmlclose}, 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Barking{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Road{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Canning{\*\xmlclose} 
